snippet.title: HSD TOWNDAY EN
snippet.description:
Hello Sweet Days English Launch.
Make your own special look with items featuring Sanrio characters!
Exchange invitations with your friends for parties with special Sanrio guests!
The English Launch will be celebrated with special commemorative items and prizes.
Download Hello Sweet Days now!
